longBusinessSummary: Attendo AB (publ) provides health and care services in Scandinavia and Finland. The company offers nursing homes for people with dementia or physical care requirements; home care services, including care, meals, cleaning, laundry, evening and night, and home health care services; and homes for people of various ages with a range of disabilities or care needs. It also provides respite care and companion services, as well as short term accommodation; personalized care for people with neuropsychiatric and psychosocial impairments; and social-worker supported foster care, crisis and emergency accommodation, HVB-homes, addiction care, and various forms of supportive housing services, as well as rehabilitation care services. The company was founded in 1985 and is headquartered in Danderyd, Sweden.
